  <summary date="2021-01-29T19:16:30Z" status="Introduced in House">Small Refinery Exemption Fairness Act of 2019

This bill revises requirements under the renewable fuel program to adjust the renewable fuel obligation to account for the full volume of gasoline and diesel produced by exempted small refineries of crude oil. The renewable fuel program requires transportation fuel to contain a minimum volume of renewable fuel.</summary>
